{"about_the_game":"Ativeil is a fun and interesting 3D puzzle game. Cubes, lasers, teddy bears... this game has them all. Kick your brain into high gear as you try to solve each puzzle, whilst listening to the relaxing music. Take your time to examine the many puzzles that are presented to you and learn the mechanics that will help you solve them and reach your goal.<br>Can you figure it out ?<br><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>5 Unique Zones</strong> : Each zone has a unique visual theme and contains a different category of puzzles (logic,abstract,physical,movement, etc..)<br></li><li> <strong>Over 80 puzzles</strong> based on a number of unique mechanics.<br></li><li> <strong>Atmospheric environments</strong> and locales will keep your exploring interesting and enjoyable.<br></li><li> <strong>No mainline narrative</strong> : No need to go talk to guy 'A' to pick key 'X' and unlock door 'Y'.<br></li><li> <strong>No blocking puzzles</strong> : You are free to move from room to room and from puzzle to puzzle without any restrictions. Can't solve or don't like a puzzle? move to the next!<br></li><li> <strong>No pressure</strong> : There are no timers and no time-tracking or scoring based on time/speed, solve them at your own pace.<br></li><li> <strong>No punishment</strong> : You are encouraged to experiment and play around with the mechanics in order to figure out each puzzle. No death counters or penalty for failure.<br></li><li> <strong>Multiple solutions</strong> : Most puzzles have more the one way to solve them. Your creativity and imagination is the limit.<br></li><li> <strong>Relaxing music</strong> : Relaxing music will always be playing in the background. Make yourself a cup of tea and enjoy some good puzzle time.<br></li><li> <strong>Achievements</strong> : Need an extra challenge? try to find all missing teddy bears and unlock all achievements</li></ul><br><br><strong>About gameplay : </strong><br>Ativeil is a strongl